  <title xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">CSR-konference / PPD-workshop marts 2015</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The overall development goal of the project is to contribute to the promotion of Corporate Social Responsibility and sustainable global value chains. 

The immediate objective of the project is to organise and co-host a high-level international conference on sustainable global value chains through Public Private Dialogue. The organisation of this event is carried out in cooperation with DI and World Bank Group. The conference will take place in connection with the 8th Public Private Dialogue Workshop in Copenhagen from 10-13 March 2015, recurring workshop for PPD-practitioners from approximately 20 countries who will also follow the conference to take stock of recent developments in Public Private Dialogue knowledge, explore how dialogue can foster inclusive and sustainable development, and help build developing countries&apos; capacity to effectively manage and monitor green growth reform processes.</narrative>
  </description>
